:R-HSA-3134975  a           obo:GO_0032479 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "Innate immune responses are coordinated and regulated to provide an efficient first line of defense against pathogens and at the same time to prevent host self-damage. Here we present some regulatory events involved in the detection of cytosolic nucleic acids." ;
